tafsir[53]{c,v,t}:
  42,1,"Haa, Miim : firo sugu Й—ee kalfe yawtiino ka fuЙ—Й—orde cortewol Al-baqarah."
  42,2,"Ain, Siin, Qaaf: firo sugu Й—ee kalfe yawtiino ka fuЙ—Й—orde cortewol Al-baqarah."
  42,3,"Ko sugu oo wayahu woni ko Allah wahayiniri e maa an Muhammdu, e Й“en AnnabaaЙ“e Makko adinooЙ“e ma, Allah FooluЙ—o e yaggingol ayЙ“e Mun, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o e toppitannde Mun e tagu Mun."
  42,4,"Ko Kanko Allah tun, woni ko jeyi kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi: tagugol e laamagol toppitoo. Ko Kanko kadi woni ToowuЙ—o e jaati Mun, fotde mum, poolgu e kattal Mun e toppitagol Mun, MawnuЙ—o e jaati Mun."
  42,5,"Hino jeyaa e mawngu Allah ngun, tawde kammuuli Й—in e no Й—i foti e waade e toowude, hiЙ—i eЙ“Й“a seekorgol dow leydi ndin, hara Malaa'ika'en no laЙ“Й“inira Joomi maЙ“Й“e, yettugol Mo, yankinanoo Mo mawnina Mo, Й“e toroo Mo haforangol wonЙ“e ka leydi Й“en. Awa anndee pellet, ko Allah woni Haforanoowo kala tuubuЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, HinnotooЙ—o Й“e."
  42,6,"ЖҒen jogitiiЙ“e sanamuuji yiЙ—Й“e reweteeЙ—i hara wanaa Allah, Allah na tommbii kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, O yoЙ“itoyay Й“e Й—e. An non NulaaЙ—o, a wonaali fawaaЙ—o reenugol golle maЙ“Й“e, tawde a lamnditortaake kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en. An on, ko a yottinoowo tun."
  42,7,"Ko wano Men wahayinirnoo e Й“eya AnnabaaЙ“e adinooЙ“e ma Й“en, Men wahayiniri e maaЙ—a an NulaaЙ—o, janngeteende e haala aarabu, fii ko jertiniraa yimЙ“e Makka Й“en e aarabuuЙ“e wonЙ“e takko mayre Й“en, refti yimЙ“e Й“en fow. Jertinaa kadi yimЙ“e Й“en, fii Г‘alande Darngal, Гұalnde Allah mooЙ“oyta adinooЙ“e e sakkitiiЙ“e fow nokku gooto, fii Гұaaweede yoЙ“ee; Гұalaande nde sikke alaa e mu'un. YimЙ“e Й“en wonoyay pecce Й—iЙ—i: feccere goo, ka Aljanna; woni muumini'en, ndeya feccere, ka Yiite; woni heeferЙ“e Й“en."
  42,8,"Si Allah haajuno, O waЙ—ayno fow e mofte goote ka lislaamu, O naada Й“e fow kadi Aljana. Kono ГұenЖҙal Makko ngal eЙ“Й“ii nde O naadata mo O muuyi ka lislaamu, ontigi naatoya Aljanna. TooГұuЙ“e non ko'e-mun geddi e keeferaaku, Й“e alaa giЙ—o heftoowo fii maЙ“Й“e, wanaa walloowo Й“e e lepte Allah Й—en."
  42,9,"Si ko woni, Й“ee sirkooЙ“e jogiti yiЙ—Й“e goo, ko wanaa Allah. Hara non ko Allah woni GiЙ—o On tigiri, wanaa goЙ—Й—o goo nafatah maa lorra. Ko Kanko woni wuurnitoowo maayЙ“e Й“en, fii hasbugol Й“e yoЙ“a Й“e, huunde ronkintaa Mo."
  42,10,"Onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, kala ko luutondirЙ—on e fii mun ka doose diina maa ka calЙ—i mun, haray Гұaawoore mun nden, ko ka Allah woni: on ruttoto ka Deftere Makko maa ka Sunna NulaaЙ—o Makko on (yo o his). Ko On siforЙ—o Й—in sifaaji, woni Joomi am; ko e Makko mi fawi fii am on fow, ko ka Makko kadi mi ruttorta tuubugol."
  42,11,"Ko Allah tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, no Й—i anndiranooka. O waЙ—irani on e pittaali mon Й—in genndooЙ“e, O waЙ—ani on e gelooЙ—i Й—in e na'i Й—in e dammi Й—in nooneeji, no Й—i Й—uuЙ—ira fii mon. Himo tagira on e ko O waЙ—irani on genndiraaЙ“e kon, O wuurnira on e ko O waЙ—irani on e tebeeli e Й“ira neemoraaЙ—i mon Й—in. Hay huunde e tagu tagu Makko ngun yerondiraa e Makko. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo haala jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, Yi'oowo kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en; huunde e mun laawotaako Mo. Ma O yoЙ“itoy Й“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en: ko moЖҙЖҙi e ko boni."
  42,12,"Ko Kanko tun heerori soktirЙ—e ngaluuji kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Himo yaajnana arsike on mo O muuyani e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, fii ndaarndagol si ontigi yettay Mo kaa o yedday; ko wano non kadi O Й“illinirta mo O muuyani, jarribagol annda si ontigi muГұГұoto kaa o tikkiray senndoore Allah nden. Pellet, ko O AnnduЙ—o kala huunde. Hay huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo, e nafata jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en."
  42,13,"O sar'inanii on e diina kan, sugu ko O yamirnoo kon Nuuhu yottingol gollitiri, e kon ko Men wahayini e maaЙ—a, an NulaaЙ—o. O sar'inani on kadi, sugu ko Men yamirnoo kon Ibraahiima, e Muusaa e Iisaa'en fow yo yottin gollitira, wonnde: ГұiiЙ“inee diina kan; hara on seertaali e makka. Kono ko noddataa sirkooЙ“e Й“en e mun kon, yo Й“e bajjinЙ—in Allah, woЙ—Й—itoo e sirku, Й—um mawnii e dow maЙ“Й“e. Allah non, Himo suЙ“oo e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, O hawrindida Й—um ko rewa Mo Й—oftoo Mo, O fewna kala tuuboowo yiltoo e junuubi mun."
  42,14,"HeeferЙ“e Й“en e sirkuЙ“e Й“en seertaano, si wanaa Й“aawo nde hujja on ГұiiЙ“irde e dow maЙ“Й“e, nuleede Muhammadu (jom kisiyee) sabu bewre e tooГұd. Si wanaano sabu fii Allah anndiino wonnde O nennanayЙ“e lepte Й—en haa e happu mo O anndi; woni Г‘alnde Darngal, ko pellet, O Гұaawayno hakkunde maЙ“Й“e; O jippinira lepte Й—en e maЙ“Й“e, sabu yeddugol Й“e ngol Allah, fenna NulaaЙ—o Makko on. Pellet, Alyahuuda roninaaЙ“e Tawreeta Й“en, e Annasaara roninaaЙ“e Linjiila Й“en Й“aawo Й“eya, e kala arnooЙ“e Й“aawo sirkooЙ“e Й“en, fow e maЙ“Й“e no sikkitii ndee Alqur'aanaare, nde Muhammadu ardi e mun, fennuЙ“e mo."
  42,15,"Noddan kaa diina ГұiiЙ“uka; tabitiraa e Й—um, no Allah yamirmaa non; wata a jokku mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e meerente Й—en, maakanaa Й“e tuma wennjondiral: mi gomЙ—inii Allah, e kala Deftere nde O jippini e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. O yamirii lam, yo mi Гұaawir nunЙ—al hakkunde mon. Ko Allah Mo mi rewata on, woni Joomi am e Joomi mon on fow. Ko menen golle amen - moЖҙЖҙe maa bonЙ—e - woodani, ko onon kadi golle mon - moЖҙЖҙe maa bonЙ—e woodani. Yeddondiral woo alaa hakkunde amen e mon, Й“aawo hujja on Й“anngude. Allah mooЙ“oyay en fow men. Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde nden Г‘alnde Darngal; O yoЙ“ita kala e men, ko hanndi kon. Ontuma non, laaЙ“ay ko hommbo goongi, oya feni."
  42,16,"ЖҒen wennjirooЙ“e hujjaaji meerente e diina Allah jippinaaka e Muhammadu kan, Й“aawo nde yimЙ“e Й“en nootaade ka, hujja Й“en on, ko meere yanoowo ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e e ka gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en; Й“aЙ—te woo alanaa mo. Tikkere Allah hino fawii Й“e, sabu yeddugol Й“e ngol saloo goonga, hino woodani Й“e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e, sabbitiiЙ—e Й“e Г‘alnde Darngal."
  42,17,"Ko Allah woni jippinirЙ—o Alqur'aanaare nden goonga, mo sikke alaa e mu'un, O jippini kadi fii nunЙ—al, ko Гұaawiree hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en. Hino hasii hara Darngal, ngal Й“ee fennata fii mun ngal, ko ko Й“adii. Hino anndaa non, wonnde kala ko arata, ko ko hewti."
  42,18,"ЖҒe gomЙ—inaa Й“en Darngal, hino Й—aЙ“Й“a yaccingol fii maggal; tawde Й“e gomЙ—inaa fii hasboore wanaa warjeede wanaa fii lepte. GomЙ—imЙ“e Allah Й“en kan, ko Й“e hulu Й“e fii maggal, e hoore hiЙ“e felliti wonnde ko ngal goonga, mo sikke alaa e mu'un. Awa anndee wonЙ“e yeddondireede Й“en e fii Darngal, hara hiЙ“e sikkitii daragol maggal, ko pellet, Й“e wonii e nder majjere woЙ—Й—unde goonga."
  42,19,"Allah ko newaniiЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Himo yaacnana arsika mo O muuyani e maЙ“Й“e, O Й“illina mo O muuyani, ka yurmegol mo; hay si goЙ—Й—um goo yaltitii. Ko Kanko woni DoolnuЙ—o Mo gooto foolataa, JaaliiЙ—o yagginoowo ayЙ“e Makko Й“en."
  42,20,"Kala tawЙ—o ko baraaje ndun laakara o faaliraa golle makko Й—en, Men sowanay mo mbarjaari makko ndin; moЖҙЖҙere kala, sappo yeru mun, haa hewta cowalle teemeЙ—Й—e jeeЙ—iЙ—i, haa Й“ura Й—on ko Й—uuЙ—i. Kala kadi tawЙ—o ko jayru ndun aduna tun o faalaa, Men okkay mo geЙ“al makko ngal, yeru makko on; hara non o alaa ka laakara ton, hay geЙ“al, tawde o Й“uurnii aduna e dow laakara."
  42,21,"Kaa hara kafidaaЙ—i e Alalh hino woodani Й“ee sirkooЙ“e, sar'inanЙ—i Й“e e diina kan, kon ko Allah duЕӢaaki fi mun: harmingol ko dagii, maa dagingol ko harmi? Si wanaano fii ngola Konngol ngol Allah happunoo e mun, dumunna senndugoygol hakkunde luutondirЙ“e Й“en, e tawde O nennanay Й“e haa nden Гұlande, O Гұaawayno hakkunde maЙ“Й“e kisan. Ko pellet, hino woodani tooГұirЙ“e ko'e-mun Й“en sirkangol Allah yedda Mo, lepte muusuЙ—e, Г‘alnde Darngal."
  42,22,"A yi'ay an NulaaЙ—o, tooГұirЙ“e ko'e-mun Й“en sirku e geddi, hiЙ“e huliri leptireede ko Й“e faggitii kon e bakkaatu, hara le Й—um yantay e maЙ“Й“e, feere mun alaa, nafa woo alaa e ko Й“e hulirta Й—um. ЖҒen non gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, Й“en no seedi e Й“eya; Й“ee Й—oo hino e nder naakooji Aljanna, hiЙ“e neeminora ton, kala ko Й“e faalaa ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e; neemaaji Й—i taЖҙondirtaa haa pooma. Ko Й—um tigiri, woni Й“ural mawnungal, ngal alaa nanndo."
  42,23,"Ko ngon welo-welo mawngo, woni ko Allah wewlinirta jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, e junngo NulaaЙ“e Makko on; Й“en jeyaaЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe. An NulaaЙ—o, maaku: mi Й—aЙ“Й“iraa on njoЙ“di woo, e ko mi yottinta kon, si wanaa njoЙ“di wootiri, ndi nafitorton onon; ndin woni: nde yiЙ—orton lam, fii ko mi enЙ—am mon. Kala faggitiiЙ—o moЖҙЖҙere, Men Й“eydanay mo njoЙ“di e hoore mayre: moЖҙЖҙere nden, ko sappo yeru mayre. Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo junuubi kala tuubuЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, mantoowo golle maЙ“Й“e moЖҙЖҙe Й—en Й—e Й“e gollirta fii Makko."
  42,24,"Hini jeyaa e ko sirkooЙ“e Й“en aaЖҙii, wonnde Muhammadu (yo o his) fefindi ndee Alqur'aanaare, o dammbi nde e Joomi makko. Allah ruttiiri Й“e wiide: hara a aru fefindaade fenaande woo, Ma Mi notu e Й“ernde maa nde, Mi meha meere fefindaande nden, Mi heddina goonga kan. Nde tawnoo non, wanaa non woniri, Й—um tinndinii wonnde Annabiijo on (yo o his) ko wahayu Joomi makko o wonndi e mun. Pellet le, ko O AnnduЙ—o ko woni e Й“erЙ—e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e mum."
  42,25,"Ko Kanko Allah woni jaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee jeyaaЙ“e Makko yedduЙ“e Й“en, si Й“e ruttike e Makko, O yawtana Й“e bonЙ—i Й—i Й“e faggitii Й—in, e hoore Himo anndi kala ko huuwoton. Huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e golle mon Й—en. Ma O yoЙ“itoy on Й—e."
  42,26,"Himo jaabina toraare gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ—o Mun on, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, O Й“eydana Й“e e ko Й“e lamndaaki mo kon, ka Й“ural Makko. YedduЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ—o Mun Й“en non, hino woodani Й“e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e, habbitiiЙ—e Й“e Г‘alnde Darngal."
  42,27,"Si tawno Allah yaГұГұanno jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en fow arsike, ko pellet, Й“e bewirayno tooГұe ka hoore leydi; kono Himo jippinira arsike on, emmbere ko O muuyi yaГұГұude O Й“illina. Pellet, ko O humpitiiЙ—o fii jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, ReenuЙ—o Й“e. O okkiray ГұeГұЖҙal Makko ngal, O Й“illinira ngal kadi."
  42,28,"Ko Kanko woni jippinoowo ndiyam Й—am e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, Й“aawo Й“e taЖҙaade fii majjam, O saaka Й—am ndiyam, Й—am fuЙ—ina leydi ndin. Ko Kanko kadi woni GiЙ—o heftuЙ—o fii maЙ“Й“e, YettiniiЙ—o e kala fiyaakyu."
  42,29,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji tindinayЙ—i e kattal e gootaagu Makko ngun: tagugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e Й—in ruugayЙ—i haawniiЙ—i, Й—i O saakiti hakkunde majji. Kanko e fii mooЙ“indiroygol Й“e ngol Гұaawa Й“e yoЙ“ita Й“e, nde O haaji e mun woo, ko O hattanЙ—o. O ronkataa fii mun, wano woniri O ronkaano tagugol Й“e ka arannde laawol."
  42,30,"Kala ko heЙ“i on, onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, immorde e musiiba wonkiijii mon maa e jawle mon, ko sabu geddi Й—i juuЙ—e mon Й—en faggitii. Allah non, hino yaafoo ko Й—uuЙ—i e mun, hara O nanngitirtaa on Й—in."
  42,31,"On wonaa hattanЙ“e laawagol lepte Joomi Й—en, si O faandanike on Й—e; On maraa kadi yawti Mo Kanko, woni giЙ—o hettoowo fii mon, wanaa ballo faabotooЙ—o on e lepte Makko Й—en, si O faandanii mon Й—e."
  42,32,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji tinndinayЙ—i e kattal e gootaagu Makko ngun: laaЙ—e dogayЙ—e Й—en ka maayo, toowirЙ—e wa pelle."
  42,33,"Si O haajii deeЖҙingol henndu naЙ“ay ndu laaЙ—e Й—en, O waЙ—ay; ndu waЙ—tina ontuma, tabitu ndu e hoore maayo ngon. Woni e ko jantaa koo, maandeeji Й“annginЙ—i kattal Allah ngal, wonannde kala muГұГұotooЙ—o jarrabuyee, yettoowo neema Allah on e dow mun."
  42,34,"Si Mo yiЙ—i Kanko Allah, O yooliray Й—en laaЙ—e, wurtugol heenndu tiiЙ—undu e majje, sabu bakkaatu ko yimЙ“e Й“en faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non, ko Й—uuЙ—i e bakkatuuji jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en."
  42,35,"Tuma O halkirta laaЙ—e Й—en henndu ndun, wennjaynooЙ“e e Aayeeje Allah Й—en, fii bonnitugol Й—e, hiЙ“e wonnde ontuma, wonnde alaa no Й“e laawora e halkaare nden."
  42,36,"Kala huunde nde hokkaЙ—on onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, woni ko jaahu maa Й“iЙ—Й—o, haray ko dakamme nguurndam aduna, ko ko fii mun lannata; neema duumotooЙ—o on, ko neema Aljanna on mo Allah marani gomЙ—imЙ“e Mo Й“en, Й“e gomЙ—ini NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, hara ko e Joomi maЙ“Й“e tun, woni Й“e fawotoo e fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e kala."
  42,37,"ЖҒen woЙ—Й—itotooЙ“e e junuubi mawЙ—i Й—in e pankare Й—en, si wonii Й“e tikkanii fawГұoriiЙ—o Й“e konngol maa kuugal, hara Й“e yaaforay ontigi e Й—um, sabu moЖҙЖҙere e maslaha ko woni e mun."
  42,38,"ЖҒen nootoriiЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, huuwugol ko O yamiri Й“e, woЙ—Й—itoo e ko O haЙ—i Й“e, ГұiЙ“nir Й“e julde nden no timmiri, Й“e tawata ko diisondirayЙ“e hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, e kala fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e, wintotorayЙ“e fii Allah, e kon ko Men arsiki Й“e."
  42,39,"E Й“en tawЙ“e si tooГұe yanii e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e yottoray teddingol hoore maЙ“Й“e, tuma tawi hara tooГұuЙ—o on hanndaa e yaafeede. Nden yottannde, ko jojjunde, teЕӢtinii si nafa alaa e yaafagol ngol."
  42,40,"Kala faalaaЙ—o yottaade, ko hakkee makko. Ko woni tun, hara ko yeru mun, ko aldaa e Й“eydugol maa fantingol. Kala non yaafiiЙ—o boniiЙ—o e mun, o moЖҙЖҙintini hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, haray njoЙ“di makko ndin ko ka Allah woni. Pellet non, O yiЙ—aa tooГұirooЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“en, ka wonikiiji e ka jawle e guri maЙ“Й“e; Himo aГұi Й“en."
  42,41,"Kala non yottiiЙ—o, ko Й“en woni Й“e nanngitirtaake ko waЙ—i kon."
  42,42,"Ka nanngitireede lepte fawii e mun, ko tooГұooЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“en, hara hiЙ“e huuwa geddi e leydi ndin: Й“en Й—on, lepte muusuЙ—e hino woodani laakara."
  42,43,"MuГұГұiiЙ—o on kadi o yaafii tooГұe Й—en, ko pellet, moЖҙЖҙere ngal muГұal Й—on, yiltoto e makko wonndude e renndo ngon. ЖҠum ko fiyaaku yettiniiЙ—o, ko jom-geЙ“al mawngal tun, woni ko hawrondirta e Й—um."
  42,44,"Kala mo Allah hoyni gaa e peewal haa O majjini ontigi e goonga kan, haray giЙ—o goo alanaa mo, mo no heftana mo fiyakuuji makko Й—in. A tinay tooГұirnooЙ“e ko'e mun Й“en geddi e keeferaaku, tuma Й“e yi'i lepte Й—en Г‘alnde Darngal, hiЙ“e yeloo wi'a: hara laawol ruttorde aduna no woodi, men tuubana Allah?"
  42,45,"A tinay kadi an NulaaЙ—o, Й“ee tooГұuЙ“e hino weeЙ“itee e Yiite ngen, hara ko Й“e hoynaaЙ“e jaasinaa, hiЙ“e ndaarira yimЙ“e Й“en, lepaarol, hakkee ko Й“e huli nge. GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en wi'ay ontuma: ko woni hayruЙ“e Й“en tigiri, ko hayrimЙ“e ko'e mun Й“en e Й“eynguureji mun Й—in Г‘alnde Darngal, sabu ko Й“e hawri kon e lepte Allah Й—en. Awa anndee pellet, tooГұirЙ“e ko'e mun Й“en geddi e keeferaaku, Й“e wonii e lepte duumiiЙ—e poomaa."
  42,46,"YiЙ—Й“e alanaa Й“e,ko wallitoo Й“e daЙ—ugol lepte Allah Й—en,Г‘alnde Darngal.Kala non mo Allah majjini e goonga kan,haray o heЙ“ataa ko tinndina mo e maggal, haa poomaa."
  42,47,"Onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, nootee Joomi mon, tinnorgol e ko O yamiri kon, woЙ—Й—itoo e ko O haЙ—i kon, acca kadi caate, ado Г‘alaande Darngal nden arde on, nde tawata ruttoowo alanaa nde. Nden Гұalnde, fattorde woo alanaa on, yeddugol junuubi mon Й—in ko faggita ka kadi alanaa ton."
  42,48,"Si Й“e Й—uurnike e ko yamirЙ—aa Й“e kon, haray Men nuliraali ma an NulaaЙ—o, aynugol kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e: fawaaki ma, si wanaa yottingol nulal ngal e maЙ“Й“e, Гұaawoore maЙ“Й“e nden, ko ka Allah woni. Si wonii Men meeЙ—inirii neЙ—Й—anke on neema ngalu e callal ekn, o wewlira Й—um; si bone non woni memiei Й“e sanu junuubi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, a taway ko Й“e anndiraaЙ“e dullangol Allah, ronka yettude neemaaji Makko Й—in, Й“e wona e tikkangol ko O hoddirani Й“e kon ГұeГұЖҙal Makko."
  42,49,"Ko Allah heeranii laamagol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Himo tagira worЙ“e e rewЙ“e maa ko wanaa Й—um, no O haajiri. Himo yeЙ—a mo O muuyani Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e, O Й—ala ontigi Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e, ko non kadi O yeЙ—irta mo O muuyani Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e, O Й—ali mo Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e, maa O waЙ—ana mo O muuyani kadi Й“iЙ—Й“e e worЙ“e, O waЙ—a mo O muuyani wonnde mo jibintaa. Pellet, Himo anndi ko fewndii e ko saatii. Ko Й—um woni timmugol ganndal e ГұeГұЖҙal Makko. Huunde wirnanaaki Mo. Wanaa goЙ—Й—um kadi rontinta Mo."
  42,50,"42:49"
  42,51,"Sellantaa neЙ—Й—anke, nde Allah yewtata, si wanaa hara ko wahayu maa ko nanndi, maa hara ko no o nanirta yewtere Makko nden, tawa o sutaaki mo, maa O immina Malaa'ikaajo e makko, wano Jibiriilu, on wahayina e neЙ—Й—anke NulaaЙ—o on, ko Allah duЕӢanii mo kon. Pellet, Kanko Allah, ko O ToowuЙ—o e Jaati e Sifaaji Makko, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o e tagu e kattal e sari'a Makko on."
  42,52,"Ko wano Men wahayinirnoo non e AnnabaaЙ“e adinooЙ“e ma Й“en, Men wahayiniri Alqur'aana e maaЙ—a, an NulaaЙ—o, e yamiroore Amen. A anndaano ko woni Defte jippiiЙ—e Й—en e Й“eya NulaaЙ“e, a anndaano kadi ko woni gomЙ—inal; si ko woni, Men jippinin ndee Alqur'aanaare, ko nde ndayginnde, ndaygu ngu Men fewnirta mo Men muuyani e jeyaaЙ“e Amen Й“en. Pellet, ko a fewnoowo yimЙ“e Й“en, e laawol focciingol, woni diina lislaamu kan."
  42,53,"Laawol Allah, On jeyЙ—o ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi, taguЙ—o laamii toppitii Й—i. Anndee pellet, ko ka Allah tun, woni ko fiyakuuji Й—in ruttotoo, ka eЙ“Й“ugol topiitoo."
